      "review_summary": "The PR adds Feishu drive list pagination inputs, an automatic list-all mode, paginated info lookup with optional folder scope, regression tests, and drive skill docs for list pagination.\n\nPR surface: Source +58, Tests +213, Docs +14. Total +285 across 4 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. Current main has a source-level reproduction: list has no cursor input, listFolder calls the Lark list API once, and getFileInfo searches one page before File not found; live tenant proof was not run in this read-only review.",
